[[File:Ice-on-a-stick.jpg|thumb|right|250px|The [[Snow King]] is presented with an ice-on-a-stick.]]
'''Ice-on-a-stick''' was a consumable item. It played a crucial role in the [[skirmish at the Snow Palace]] on the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon of Endor]]. When several young [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] infiltrated the [[Snow Palace|palace]] to take the [[season scepter]] from the disillusioned [[Snow King]], [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Warrick]] conceived the idea of disguising himself and his friend [[Latara/Legends|Latara]] as ice-on-a-stick peddlers. The Snow King fell for Warrick's trick, dropping the season scepter when he reached for the frozen treat.

